Class Invader

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node

edu.vanier.spaceshooter.entities.Invader
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class Invader extends Sprite
Basic invader with 1 HP All parameters used to create invader and the sprite associated Type is enemy Stack pane for dimensions of the window Boolean left, right, up, down are used to move around the sprite
